  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2777230/extras/7cd80d2b822ee980f1574352521c50c9.webp?t=1724562327\" width=666 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2777230/extras/f45fc60adbf986e3516ada722013d4a9.avif?t=1724562327\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The slaves of Alaa-Mogus have become brutal in our world, <strong>URAANKHAI</strong>, we need to put them in their place<br><br></li><li>Letnik, Tuymaad Valley, Holiday Glade, Lake Saysar - our sacred places must be protected from Alaa-Mogus<br><br></li><li>Translations into Yakut and English languages<br><br></li><li>Don’t forget to drink <strong>BYYRPAKH</strong> and <strong>KYMYS</strong> for health and strength<br><br></li><li><strong>YAKUT</strong> phonk in repertoire<br><br></li><li>Use different <strong>YAKUT</strong> techniques to shred the devils from the lower world<br><br></li><li>FIGHT the evil spirits from the <strong>OLONKHO</strong> epic face to face<br><br></li><li>Use various Yakut tools, such as a knife, batas, batyya, etc.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2777230/extras/eaa2b6b7c8f42e44fc380725d580e8dd.avif?t=1724562327\" width=600 height=256 /></span><br><br><strong>URAANKHAI</strong> we are here?!<br><br><strong>URUY-AIKHAL! URUY-AIKHAL! URUY-AIKHAL! AYKHAL! AYKHAL!</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2777230/extras/7cd80d2b822ee980f1574352521c50c9.webp?t=1724562327\" width=666 height=40 /></span>",
